{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"final"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"visibilityAabb","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/AABB","preciseIdentifier":"s:10SwiftGodot4AABBV","text":"AABB","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Grow the box if particles suddenly appear\/disappear when the node enters\/exits the screen. The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/AABB","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be grown via code or with the "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Particles → Generate AABB"}]},{"type":"text","text":" editor tool."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GPUParticles3D\/visibilityAabb","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is overridden by "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GeometryInstance3D\/customAabb","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" if that property is set to a non-default value.","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GPUParticles3D"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GPUParticles3D\/visibilityAabb"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/gpuparticles3d\/visibilityaabb"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/AABB","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" that determines the node’s region which needs to be visible on screen for the particle system to be active. "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GeometryInstance3D\/extraCullMargin","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is added on each of the AABB’s axes. Particle collisions and attraction will only occur within this area."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"SwiftGodot"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","title":"visibilityAabb","externalID":"s:10SwiftGodot14GPUParticles3DC14visibilityAabbAA4AABBVvp","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"visibilityAabb","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10SwiftGodot4AABBV","text":"AABB"}]},"references":{"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot","title":"SwiftGodot","role":"collection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Framework to write Godot Game Extensions using the Swift Programming Language."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/GeometryInstance3D/extraCullMargin":{"role":"symbol","title":"extraCullMargin","abstract":[{"text":"The extra distance added to the GeometryInstance3D’s bounding box (","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/AABB","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":") to increase its cull box."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GeometryInstance3D\/extraCullMargin","url":"\/d